{
  "stem": "20848.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I smuggled myself out and I went to the second SS-man, I thought maybe he won't do that, maybe he would put me with the young people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How old were you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, I was, I think, 11 and 1/2 or 12, I don't know exactly. 1943-- that's four years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was [INAUDIBLE] it must have been 12 years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would have been 12 in probably in October.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in May.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I smuggled myself to the second SS-man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he did the same, he put me with women and children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they marched us off to a place surrounded with wires.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were only women and children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, from far away, I see my mother marching out of the sauna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm screaming to my mother, mama, mama, I'm going to my death-- in Polish of course.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother said-- she didn't hear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she said to me, Lusia, she said, Lusia, tell the lady who gives the frocks to give you a warm frock.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she marched off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now there were two guards at the door, at the gate, you know, seeing that nobody got out of this big yard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, I was going all the time to these two guards, saying to them, [GERMAN], which is a broken German saying, I am 16 years old and I can work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were pushing me with their guns away all the time, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I went three or four times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were pushing me all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And somehow, I-- I-- when I was saying to my mother, we're going to-- I'm going to my death, those women who knew me said, why are you saying such terrible things.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because of you, they will send us to death.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
